text.tspan: extended torch base thing for words
When possible, use Devil Breeze font for team numbers.
Text should always be White/Green on black or black on white.
Never green on white or white on green.
Use Big John on headlines and Shirts and whatever.
Use a sans-serif font as body text. The actual one doesn't matter,
but use Dosis if you want to be fancy.
Shirts and web should have black backgrounds.
Banners and prints/handouts should be white.
